data.description:
Get ready to live your best life in this desert paradise! This stunning home in the sought-after 85083 zip code is the perfect blend of chic style and desert tranquility. With 3,740 sq ft of space to play with this home is a dream.

Picture this: walk right in to new flooring that are stylish and sturdy, swanky two-tone cabinets that are straight-up Instagram-worthy. Oh, and guess what? We've got not one, but TWO bedrooms downstairs for whatever you fancy. Upstairs boast a loft, HUGE master bedroom and additional bedrooms.

Now, let's talk outdoor oasis - your backyard is practically begging for parties with pavers, turf, an above ground swimming pool, and a custom bar!

Plus, the hood is all about community vibes, and you're just a hop, skip, and a jump from schools and shopping!!
